Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.10,0:00:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, everyone, we're going to start Kaleido Star!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.94,0:00:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, you guys all\Nhave times when you're impatient too,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.27,0:00:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and you want to do\Nsomething right now, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.17,0:00:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're champing at the bit and\Nirritated that time won't go faster,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.72,0:00:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and it's just like, "Oh, come on!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I remembered how much fun the stage is\Nbecause of that performance the other day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I'm so worked up it's\Nlike I just can't stand still!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.10,0:00:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And in the midst of that now\NMr. Kenneth is opening a car show,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and I get to be in it too! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.35,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay, my batteries are fully charged!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna do my best! Best! Best!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:01:02.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss hajimari wa aka to kuro no Passion{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:09.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Toki ni urahara na kokoro o tayori ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:16.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss kirifuda wa mirai o kaeru Mission{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.85,0:01:24.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Koi ni aimai na kotae wa iranai {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:32.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arienai genjitsu minai furi shite mo Bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:38.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egatai shinjitsu\NCan U feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nesshiyasui jibun ni Say What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.31,0:01:46.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tomadou iibun {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.62,0:01:55.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' samenai yume ochiteku sadame{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:02.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.52,0:02:10.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe in U hikikae ni subete ushinatte mo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.35,0:02:17.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' Can't stop lovin' U\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:23.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.02,0:02:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I was really moved!\NSora Naegino is the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I started wanting to try
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,chasing my own dream again too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.33,0:02:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I terminate her contract,\Neven if performances are cancelled,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.19,0:02:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wherever Sora is becomes a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as if the stage itself is\Ntrying to bring Sora back to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.27,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's investigating that right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it appears as if Leon\NOswald really does hold the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.19,0:02:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.48,0:03:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mr. Kenneth?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.60,0:03:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just had a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.77,0:03:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Launching An Amazing Smile!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like she can't stand\Nto not be moving her body.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.60,0:03:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since she gave that all-out\Nperformance at the bank that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like she can't contain\Nherself even if she tries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.65,0:03:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is more Sora's style,\Nso it's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whee!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.90,0:03:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dust, go bye-bye!\NAll shiny, sparkle! All clean, yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.48,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everybody's bouncing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.48,0:03:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.94,0:03:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand! Yes! Yes! I'm on my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? For real?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.65,0:04:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real! It's for real!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.02,0:04:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, it looks like the time has come
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to put the project I've been\Nsecretly developing into action.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally going to do it, huh Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.95,0:04:20.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm going to give it a shot, sink or swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.94,0:04:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I won't try to stop you anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is numbers.\NI'd really like at least one more person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.27,0:04:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it your best shot, Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you too, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.02,0:04:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming for...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora captivated even a bank robber,\Nand in a place that wasn't even a proper stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.40,0:04:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't satisfy Leon on the stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.19,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't have the slightest\Nidea what it is I'm missing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.23,0:05:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I await your instruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's Miss Cathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.69,0:05:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Training is over, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.81,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's pointless to go any further with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.44,0:05:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.48,0:05:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that what you're thinking too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm doing my best.\NI don't know what more I should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if the only way is to call Sora\Nand try making her do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I disqualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.27,0:05:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we met in New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.27,0:05:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you said it was your dream to stand\Non the same stage as me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But at that time you couldn't answer\Nwhen I asked you what your next dream was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't answer, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.73,0:05:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this training, I've\Nfigured out what you're missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the most important thing\Nto anyone who stands on a stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:06:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you're projecting is your desperation\Nto be told the way out of this training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never once felt from you\Nany passion to entertain Cathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.63,0:06:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, what do you want\Nafter becoming Leon's partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.19,0:06:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want after defeating Sora?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want? What are\Nyou seeking from the stage?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Becoming Leon's partner" and\N"defeating Sora" are both small things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is what comes after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.31,0:06:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can tell you what that is.\NYou have to find it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you need is to know\Nthe importance of a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The importance of a smile?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did they tell us to\Ngather here for all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.31,0:06:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna and the others aren't here yet,\Nbut everyone else is assembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.02,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.64,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know this is sudden, but\Nthis selected group of members
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is going to do a performance at\Nthe Kenneth Motors New Model Event.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to have you perform too, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can go onstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:17.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! That's what Mr. Kenneth wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Really and truly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Sora?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.65,0:07:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'm really looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.94,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What you need is to know\Nthe importance of a smile.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So does that mean Sora knows it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.23,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay then, Mia, will you\Nexplain the show's setup?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops, before that, it looks\Nlike the fated day has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, are you ready? Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's have them make their appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Anna and the Amazing\NClowns! Come on down!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater. Cater. Cater. Cater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.06,0:07:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar. Pillar. Pillar. Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater. Cater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.31,0:08:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar. Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.40,0:08:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater. Sit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.26,0:08:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're gonna do this\Njust like we talked about, Clowns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.52,0:08:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.56,0:08:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater cater cater cater...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar pillar pillar pillar pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater cater cater cater...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.69,0:08:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pillar pillar pillar pillar pillar pillar...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh dear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.48,0:08:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.60,0:08:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it wrong, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.06,0:08:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you'd expect from\Nthe cornerstone of the team,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you steal the best part of the show...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The deal was that it was just\Nfor today! I'm not joining your team!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not? You should!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, is it okay for the Anna and\Nthe Clowns team to participate?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.10,0:08:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.77,0:08:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, then, it's just for this show, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.94,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.18,0:09:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, I'll explain the contents of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.15,0:09:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora... Naegino...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.48,0:09:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fall...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.73,0:09:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She might be able to\Nperfect the Angel's Maneuver...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.81,0:09:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And carry out the dream you couldn't.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.27,0:09:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sophie... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:43.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Promise me, Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Promise, eh? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true, that's the\None thing I can do for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.31,0:09:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:09:59.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Flowers? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.27,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From who? May, I suppose...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, I'm going to go out for a bit, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.65,0:10:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, okay. Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Miss Layla's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla's?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.44,0:10:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, because if I don't tell\Nher that I'm going to be onstage,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.31,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's like I'm doing it behind\Nher back, and I don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.35,0:10:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought maybe you wouldn't meet with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of what happened at the Festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.40,0:10:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wrong about you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you could dream\Nthe same dream that I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought you would pull through\Non any stage, no matter how cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.\NI pushed you too hard, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.44,0:11:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, now you\Ncan't even fight May for a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your goal wasn't being a true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.77,0:11:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a fun stage...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.69,0:11:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you say, Miss Layla, my goal\Nis a fun Kaleido Stage with no battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I haven't given up the dream\Nof being a true Kaleido Star, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.77,0:11:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're saying you're going to try to be a\Ntrue Kaleido Star without fighting anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.94,0:11:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There's no other path for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.52,0:11:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aiming for the position of Star that nobody's\Never been able to reach without fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.85,0:11:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That never even occurred to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.56,0:11:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be a more difficult\Npath than you can even imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:12:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long or how\Ndifficult the path, it's the path I chose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.27,0:12:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I've decided not to lose my way anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I won't walk the path\Nyou showed me, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.27,0:12:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you've decided, then\Nwalk for yourself the path you believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.77,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be in the\NKenneth Motors show coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm definitely going to make it a fun show!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.73,0:12:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora's eyes... They've gotten\Nback the sparkle they used to have.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is this feeling springing up inside me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.14,0:13:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then she smiled and told me\Nto walk down the path I believe in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.44,0:13:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really glad I went!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.65,0:13:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to walk firm down my own path.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.69,0:13:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not making Miss Layla worry any\Nmore than this is another reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.60,0:13:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Layla can still see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.31,0:13:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.06,0:13:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.06,0:13:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, since this will be a car show,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.06,0:13:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should dress\Nlike a Racing Queen and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.40,0:13:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The theme of the cars is "harmony with nature,"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I think I need an outfit\Nthat would blend in with nature...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blend in with nature?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.23,0:13:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As few adornments as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Few adornments?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bold concept--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.34,0:13:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bold concept. you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us meet in the dressing\Nroom tomorrow! Farewell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll try completely acting\Nlike Sora at tomorrow's show.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.27,0:14:12.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's the only path left to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right everyone, listen\Nas you're changing, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went and checked out the stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The positioning of the cars is\Na little different from the plan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:34.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are no big problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.81,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our first show for them and\Nwe haven't had any rehearsals either,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'll probably be nervous,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.98,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you do it just like we\Ndiscussed, there will be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.77,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's be calm and relaxed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.73,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.74,0:14:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's some kind of good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.31,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I have to hurry up and get changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, your name is Ken, right? Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.31,0:15:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so useless...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.98,0:15:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, please! You can't\Nsay that with so little warning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.52,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you can't cope with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trapeze team's act will\Ncompletely change, for one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you please reconsider?\NWe'll pay plenty of attention to safety...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.23,0:15:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to hear any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A member of the Kaleido\NStage was injured just recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this without a net is out of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, it looks bad if the net\Nshows onscreen when we're filming,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.10,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm putting it up as high as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. It was my mistake,\Nnot thinking of this beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, we have to think of a way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or we'll hardly be able to do\Nany of the trapeze act we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.39,0:15:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little late to be saying that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.20,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.56,0:15:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The trapezes are up a lot higher too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.56,0:16:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The building is a pyramid shape,\Nso the high part is pretty narrow, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.60,0:16:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we can't use the trampoline\Neither because the net's in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.40,0:16:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't put on much of a show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.44,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be really far from the\Naudience if we do it there, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.44,0:16:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.11,0:16:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's right! May, do\Nyou have any ropes or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.77,0:16:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Why would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.65,0:16:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought spare trapezes and\Nrope just in case something happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, really?! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is great! Thanks, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just what you'd expect\Nfrom Mr. Useful Man, Ken!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.85,0:16:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are we going to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.27,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You help too, okay May?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm going to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.34,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you want to do the\Ntrapeze with us too, Rosetta?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Me on the trapeze too?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you get off deciding this by yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.02,0:16:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, there's just\Nsomething I want Rosetta to do--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! I'll do it, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:17:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this okay? Rosetta still hasn't\Nreally done the trapeze, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.95,0:17:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but this isn't so difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.06,0:17:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best, so please let me, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.90,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For now I'll just try doing what Sora says.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.48,0:17:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, even if I fail it's Sora's fault.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.88,0:17:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we haven't got\Nmuch time before we go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, explain the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.60,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, can Sora make this stage her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or will the team break up\Nand fall apart in midair?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You call this a plan,\Nbut it's mostly ad-lib, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.40,0:17:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay. I think it'll\Ngo well if I'm with you, May.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cater. Pillar. Cater. Pillar.\NCater. Pillar. Cater. Pillar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.67,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn around, turn around,\Nturn around, turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're kind of into it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.52,0:18:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.44,0:18:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.35,0:18:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're {\i1}way {\i0}into him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now it's finally time for Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.19,0:19:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll have Sora show me everything about her!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.69,0:19:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with her? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The show's just started and\Nshe's already ad-libbing like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.71,0:19:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oo oo ah ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.15,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fine. Then I'll go too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, run, run, run...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.30,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck is that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.73,0:19:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her ad-lib moves are getting bigger and bigger.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.44,0:19:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've never seen Sora like this before.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.60,0:19:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is totally different than the\Nperformances I've seen from Sora up until now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.86,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Up until now, whenever I saw Sora performing,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought "I will beat her!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.85,0:19:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought no matter what\Nhappened, I'd make her lose to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.70,0:19:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But watching Sora's performance today, I'm\Nstarting to feel this completely different feeling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to beat Sora. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.83,0:19:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to beat her, but... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:55.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Something is different. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.23,0:19:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.40,0:20:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the real Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.17,0:20:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Sora who\Nloves the stage has come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rosetta, you're doing great!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.98,0:20:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fooled you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.31,0:20:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, that Rosetta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.52,0:20:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay May, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.56,0:20:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.35,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oo oo ah ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with that move?\NI can do a little thing like that too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're smiling... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.94,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora was always seeing scenes like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.39,0:21:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sora has the power to make this many smiles.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.56,0:21:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The importance of a smile... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.35,0:21:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.02,0:21:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cool, sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.35,0:21:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, awesome, May!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.64,0:21:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.06,0:21:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, May!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.48,0:21:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.27,0:21:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.23,0:21:52.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always sleeping, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.94,0:21:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll change your flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.77,0:22:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been curious all this\Ntime about that "Sophie"...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.06,0:22:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wondering who she is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sophie is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was in an accident, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.10,0:22:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.35,0:22:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's Kenneth Motors\Nshow was pretty amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lots of light was coming\Nin through the windows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.06,0:22:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and while I was jumping around on\Nthe trapezes, it was like I was dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was like my heart got really wide,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.77,0:22:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,like everybody else's feelings could\Nfly anywhere in the world with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understood clearly that it was\Nthe kind of show I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.44,0:22:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and May was also...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.15,0:22:49.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sekasu you ni muragaru Hard luck{\i0}
